    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi! Thanks for the contribution.\n\nI think I get the fix: instead of pushing \"null\" as the state of the history API, you want to push some default value needed by your app to work?\n\nIf that's it, then I will make it a proper generic non-turbolinks related option that other people could use (like instantsearch({getHistoryState: function() { return {turboLinks: true} }}).\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
